Package: nhs.predict
Type: Package
Title: NHS Predict
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Giovanni Tramonti
Maintainer: Giovanni Tramonti <giovanni.tramonti@ed.ac.uk>
Description:Package for batch processing of NHS Predict v2.1 values. 
            Calculates overall survival or recurrence-free survival at a specified interval (default 10 years) and treatment benefits for hormone therapy, chemotherapy, trastuzumab, bisphosphonates. Attaches results to dataframe.
            This work not affiliated with the development of Predict and its underlying statistical model.
            Details on NHS Predict can be found at: <doi:10.1186/bcr2464>
            The web version of NHS Predict: <https://breast.predict.nhs.uk/>.
            The package contains a small dataset of 50 fictional patient observations for the purpose of running examples.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: True
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
